text: The Delinquents is a 1957 American drama movie directed by first time director Robert Altman and starring Tom Laughlin, Peter Miller, Richard Bakalyan, Rosemary Howard. It was distributed by United Artists. ==Other websites== * * Category:1957 drama movies Category:1950s American drama movies Category:Movies directed by Robert Altman
